sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant BBR as Payload Processing (BBR)<br/>9004/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant Resolver as model-provider-resolver<br/>(in-memory store)
    participant Translator as api-translation<br/>(in-process)
    participant KeyInject as apikey-injection<br/>(in-memory store)
    participant NeMoReq as nemo-request-guard<br/>(optional)
    participant NeMoResp as nemo-response-guard<br/>(optional)
    participant Provider as External LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{ns}/{model-name}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>BBR: ext_proc request body<br/>gRPC/9004, plaintext (mesh mTLS)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over BBR,NeMoReq: Plugin Pipeline (Request Phase)
        BBR->>Resolver: Resolve model → provider<br/>(cached ExternalModel CR lookup)
        Resolver-->>BBR: Provider info + target model
        BBR->>Translator: Translate request body<br/>OpenAI → provider-native format
        Translator-->>BBR: Translated body + headers
        BBR->>KeyInject: Inject API credentials<br/>(cached Secret lookup)
        KeyInject-->>BBR: Auth header set
        opt NeMo Guardrails enabled
            BBR->>NeMoReq: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP, configurable
            NeMoReq-->>BBR: Allow / Block verdict
        end
    end

    BBR-->>Gateway: Mutated headers + body
    Gateway->>Provider: Translated request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+ (DestinationRule SIMPLE)<br/>Provider API key (injected header)
    Provider-->>Gateway: Provider response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Gateway->>BBR: ext_proc response body<br/>gRPC/9004, plaintext

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over BBR,NeMoResp: Plugin Pipeline (Response Phase)
        BBR->>Translator: Translate response body<br/>provider-native → OpenAI format
        Translator-->>BBR: Translated response
        opt NeMo Guardrails enabled
            BBR->>NeMoResp: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP, configurable
            NeMoResp-->>BBR: Allow / Block verdict
        end
    end

    BBR-->>Gateway: Mutated response body
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 2: ExternalProvider Reconciliation

    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note right of K8sAPI: ExternalProvider CR created/updated
    K8sAPI->>BBR: Watch event (controller-runtime)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Validate referenced Secret<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Create ExternalName Service<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceEntry<br/>(MESH_EXTERNAL, DNS resolution)
    BBR->>K8sAPI: Create DestinationRule<br/>(TLS origination, SIMPLE mode)

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 3: NeMo Guardrail Check (Optional)

    participant NeMo as NeMo Guardrails<br/>configurable port

    BBR->>NeMo: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>Request content (OpenAI or MCP format)
    NeMo-->>BBR: HTTP 200 { status: allow|block }
    BBR->>NeMo: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>Response content
    NeMo-->>BBR: HTTP 200 { status: allow|block }
